\nflux. Rich in emission lines, these objects are prime targets for the next\ngeneration of extremely large telescopes, JWST and ALMA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Sep 2011 01:59:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
