upling to singlet neutrinos that acquire large Majorana mass as a\nresult of the monodromy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Sep 2011 09:42:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Oct 2011 16:01:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
